SUMMARY:Salsa & Bachata at the Pier 60 Sugar Sand Festival
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exhilarating day of dance and music at the Salsa & Bachata at the Pier 60 Sugar Sand Festival! Experience live entertainment starting at 11 AM and grooving until 10 PM. Enjoy captivating performances by the talented Kenny Barcenas\, the vibrant Destiny Bachata Band\, and the dynamic Orquesta Infinidad. Bring your friends and family to dance the day away on the beautiful sugar sands while soaking in the lively atmosphere. Don’t miss out on this unforgettable celebration of rhythm and culture! \nThis concert is FREE!!!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-bachata-at-the-pier-60-sugar-sand-festival/
LOCATION:60 Pier Park\, 60 Pier Park\, Clearwater\, FL\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tampa
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/615838164_1473793691422991_5137804932735158201_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
