SUMMARY:"I Love Salsa" Latin Music Festival at OCC Roadhouse & Museum
DESCRIPTION:🔥🌴 I LOVE SALSA – LATIN MUSIC FESTIVAL (SPRING EDITION) 🌴🔥\nStormy Bay Entertainment brings you an unforgettable night of LIVE Latin music and celebration!\n📅 March 29th\, 2026\n📍 OCC Road House & Museum\n10575 49th Street North\, Clearwater\, FL 33762\n🎤 LIVE IN CONCERT:\n⭐ Angel Lopez (Ex Son By Four)\n🎶 Celebrating the 25th Anniversary of “A Puro Dolor”\n🔥 Also Performing:\n• Sabrosón\n• The Koko Band – Salsa for Salseros\n• Orchestra Fuego\n📻 In collaboration with El Nuevo Zol 97.1 FM\nGet ready for a full day of Salsa\, high-energy performances\, and non-stop dancing with the best Latin vibes in Tampa Bay! 💃🕺\n🎟 Info / RSVP: (813) 508-3544\n🌐 Tickets & Details: www.StormyBayTV.com�\nTag your dance crew and don’t miss one of the biggest Latin events of the spring! 🌺🔥\n#ILoveSalsa #AngelLopez #APuroDolor #LatinMusicFestival\n#StormyBayEntertainment #TampaBayEvents #SalsaTampa
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/i-love-salsa-latin-music-festival-at-occ-roadhouse-museum/
LOCATION:OCC Road House\, 10575 49th Street North\, Clearwater\, FL\, 33762\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tampa
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/636888622_1555118809955367_581990029371841306_n.jpg
