SUMMARY:Sunday de Sabrosura
DESCRIPTION:Tampa’s longest running\, original afternoon dance Sunday social. THANK YOU for keeping the passion for dance alive. \nJoin us for an afternoon of dancing at your favorite Sunday social in the heart of Ybor City. Come dance with us! \nPLEASE NOTE THE FOLLOWING: \n– No children will be allowed\, no exceptions\n– Must be 18 to enter event\n– If you are feeling under the weather and have COVID like symptoms\, please stay home.\nDISCLAIMER: ***Attend and dance at your own risk. TaToSalsa Inc\, its owners and staff\, La Herencia de Ybor\, its owner and staff will not be held liable for any sickness\, or injuries that may arise while attending this event. ***\nSunday de Sabrosura social is normally held once a month typically every 4th Sunday of the month in the heart of Ybor city at La Herencia de Ybor. It has grown to be Tampa’s favorite afternoon social\, where you’ll find the best mojitos and sangrias here. Let’s not forget great music with an awesome afternoon vibe! \nTaTo Salsa Students $10 | General Admission $15\nMusic By: Mambo Tribe\nDance Lesson\nPhotos \nParking is available in the lot behind the venue; HOWEVER\, YOU MUST PAY THE METER. We have noticed the rate has increased\, please consider parking across the street\, or in the lots on the adjacent sides of La Herencia\, they are cheaper. There is free street parking available in some areas\, please read the signs. \nThank you\, \nTaToSalsa \nATTENTION NEW ATTENDEES: \nADDRESS IS 1817 E 7TH AVE TAMPA\, FL\, 33605.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/sunday-de-sabrosura-2-2/2026-03-29/
LOCATION:La Herencia De Ybor\, 1817 E 7th Ave\, Tampa\, FL\, 33605\, US
CATEGORIES:Tampa
END:VEVENT
